•	DNS servers

Ethernet adapter Ethernet
IP address: 192.168.1.100
Subnet mask: 255.255.255.0
Default gateway: 192.168.1.1
Wireless LAN adapter WiFi

IP address: 192.168.2.100
Subnet mask: 255.255.255.0
Default gateway: 192.168.2.1



